---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 9, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Burleson Brunch House"
  description="Privacy Policy for Burleson Brunch House. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>

  <div class="pt-28 pb-14 bg-surface-container-low">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <p class="font-label uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm text-tertiary mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl italic text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-3 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="py-16 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="prose-custom space-y-10 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Burleson Brunch House is a family-owned restaurant at 2650 SW Wilshire Blvd, Burleson, TX 76028. This page explains what information we collect when you visit our website and how we use it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">If you fill out a form on our site, we collect what you type in, which may include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Your name, email address, and phone number when you contact us or request a reservation.</li>
            <li>Your preferred visit date and party size when making a reservation inquiry.</li>
            <li>Any messages or notes you include in your contact form submissions.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We may also collect basic technical information automatically when you visit, like your browser type and general location. This data is not tied to your name or any other personal details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use what you share with us to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Respond to your reservation requests, inquiries, and messages.</li>
            <li>Improve our website and dining experience.</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations where applicable.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We do <strong>not</strong> sell or share your personal information with other companies. We won't use it to send you marketing emails you didn't ask for.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our site may use basic cookies. They don't collect any personal information. You can turn them off in your browser settings and the site will still work fine.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We only keep contact form messages as long as we need to respond to you. We don't store any payment information. All payments are handled in person at the restaurant.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            Our site uses tools like Google Fonts and Google Maps. These have their own privacy policies and may collect basic usage data on their end. If that concerns you, it's worth taking a look at their policies directly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our site is not intended for children under 13. We don't knowingly collect information from minors. If you think we have, please reach out and we'll take care of it right away.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            You can ask to see, update, or delete any personal information we have on file for you. Just reach out using the contact info at the bottom of this page.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we'll change the date at the top of this page. Continuing to use the site after that means you're good with the updated version.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl italic text-primary mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>Questions about this policy? Get in touch:</p>
          <div class="mt-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 editorial-shadow border border-primary/10 space-y-2">
            <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface">Burleson Brunch House</p>
            <p>2650 SW Wilshire Blvd, Burleson, TX 76028</p>
            <a href="tel:6827301391" class="block text-primary hover:underline">(682) 730-1391</a>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

</Layout>
